  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>机器之心</span> <span>2026-03-25 11:59</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3f328a11&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F5L8bhP5dIqHnNjLQzJ1PjUl4r7I8FZa3qsR81G1LgrAvKAJW1dTEianuD660yyibXiaqxQPfqEp4XeBkXSlbSOv15zNPXmwbKcVnc1iaMQTwLIo%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>团队提出了防御性聚合策略，采用 \"最坏风险控制\" 的防御性思维，将全部注意力投入到 worst-case 的预防中。</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5703125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503474619\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4d97a0a5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWic1GuW68DykycvknmG9tyBvLRsVGY4rRKCGuKKSkOqnGrvGwXxqqDxHlia88ZCbqyicswl2HC89BcZA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">作者介绍：中科大团队包括共一作者冯源（博二）、郭浩宇（硕一）以及通讯作者谢希科（研究员），</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">致力于以简洁算法优化大模型长文本推理，曾提出 AdaKV、CriticalKV 等主流 KV Cache 压缩方法，仅需数行代码显著提升压缩效果。新作 DefensiveKV 延续这一理念，仅需两行算法改动，显著降低 KV Cache 压缩损失。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">随着大模型长上下文能力快速增长，海量 KV Cache 存储需求急剧增加，各类 KV Cache 压缩方法如雨后春笋般涌现。然而，这些方案在真实场景中的工程落地却常常陷入困境。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3055555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503539509\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0484d0ae&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqFCe5DtTUiaNyk8wlibwVvibo8E2dX6o9ppgr0hmbwF6LTcEJR65Kj8CiaEW56SyL98fMuUgLjT7HRsOmcLMicOqhWehmhsRRfgx2icg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;color: rgb(123, 12, 0);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">论文标题：DefensiveKV: Taming the Fragility of KV Cache Eviction in LLM Inference</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;color: rgb(123, 12, 0);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">论文链接：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://openreview.net/forum?id=nJgS06sX3O\" target=\"_blank\">https://openreview.net/forum?id=nJgS06sX3O</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;color: rgb(123, 12, 0);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">代码链接：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/FFY0/DefensiveKV/tree/main\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/FFY0/DefensiveKV/tree/main</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">中科大研究团队在 ICLR 2026 的论文 DefensiveKV: Taming the Fragility of KV Cache Eviction in LLM Inference 中给出了答案：KV Cache 压缩领域的底层假设存在根本性缺陷！当前主流方法都基于一个核心假设：KV Cache 的重要性在不同时间段是稳定的。因此它们不约而同地选择观测一段历史窗口内的平均重要性，并据此淘汰 \"不重要\" 的 cache。然而，研究团队惊讶地发现，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">这一看似合理的稳定性假设在真实场景中十</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">分脆</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">弱！&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过深入分析大模型在真实长文本任务上的行为，团队观察到一个令人震惊的现象：尽管平均观测重要性指标在绝大多数时候能够准确反映 cache 的真实重要性，但在某些特定区间却会显著失效，甚至完全反转！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.28498985801217036\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1972\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503539510\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a4c58689&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqFY2y32ZBL88DUHC8cQEiarU2hG9bYNUHUmTqsR4HrtWfmRia9FxMnRvJiaUZbLAvA1gWbDODUJXPVpeTMlEHrGjVYtl1op5rRwq4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">图 1：稳定性假设失效现象</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如上图所示，蓝色曲线代表按照平均重要性保留的一半 \"重要\" Cache。虽然绝大部分时刻这一半的 cache 能保持整体 90% 以上的真实重要性，但在特定时刻（如第 200-300 时间步），保留的 cache 甚至无法达到全部 cache 50% 的真实重要性！这种” 稳定性崩溃 \" 绝非偶发，在单次回复中竟出现高达 65 次之多。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.20777479892761394\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1492\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503539511\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=97cce3db&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqEibjtxU5luA4opsjNqgnYgxM8KgdwZSx1ianhtlzu3hwLhV1y0jjJvssVBBlxtKp5TuppKGzwhgjfho3wTFxZWZvTjZkKuBOdicc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">图 2：稳定性崩溃统计</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这揭示了一个深刻的认知盲区：以往工作过分信任 \"平均情况\"，却忽视了真实部署中最致命的最坏风险。正如金融领域的经典教训 —— 只优化平均收益而忽视极端风险的策略注定失败。当稳定性假设在关键时刻失效时，使用平均值作为压缩指示器就像在薄冰上行走，随时可能坠入深渊。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">针对这一根本性缺陷，团队提出了革命性的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">防御性聚合（Defensive Aggregation）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">策略。这一策略彻底颠覆了传统的 \"平均优化\" 范式，转而采用 \"最坏风险控制\" 的防御性思维 —— 不再关注平均损失，而是将全部注意力投入到 worst-case 的预防中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在重塑关注点之后，团队提出了一个极简的优雅设计 —— 核心算法仅需</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">两行代码</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">即可实现：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.20925925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503539512\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=148dba97&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqEKJf4DJNnuT96uceQfZ9CBicRmHnQsPWAeVw3wXt9nuxRGO8BJ6NTDtia8aXyHVpZY1opf69ic5JyylSm9nicZaBtjjuE6DbCicmn0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">图 3：核心算法仅需两行代码</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">第一步：最坏风险估计（Worst-case Risk Estimation）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">团队从风险控制角度重新思考驱逐策略 —— 驱逐一个 KV cache 的最大风险等价于它在未来可能达到的最大重要性。由于未来不可知，团队巧妙地用历史观察中的最大值来估计这一风险：只要一个 cache 在任一历史时刻表现重要，就将其视为高风险而保留。这个看似简单的 \"取最大\" 操作，却能精准捕获那些可能在未来关键时刻大放异彩的 token。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">第二步：自适应先验风险修正（Adaptive Prior-Risk Correction）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">考虑到最坏风险估计中的观测次数有限（通常仅 32 次），可能遗漏一些关键的风险。团队受贝叶斯估计中 Laplace 平滑启发，提出了一种基于先验的观测风险修正机制：计算每个注意力头中所有 KV cache 的平均观测风险作为先验风险。当某个 cache 的观测风险低于该注意力头中所有 cache 的平均风险时，自动用先验风险进行修正，防止因观测不足而遗漏高风险 cache，提供更保守的保护。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这两步操作均为线性时间，计算复杂度与传统平均值聚合相同，却带来了质的飞跃：图中防御性聚合（红色曲线）相较于之前的平均值聚合（蓝色曲线），几乎完全消除了离群点，将最坏情况下保留的重要性分数从 0.45 提升至 0.65。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.2777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503539514\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fb8a7cca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqEeiaKazhRp1Fia5BwUIicTIsAQ4TzxbumJrnPK7dS4BZvR8GecOItHWQ9Xiat7yPWyVuEcP5G07LdJ7DdxTOFRQoSGw6iccLBejH8A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">图 4：Defensive Aggregation（红色曲线）有效对抗脆弱假设，消除离群点</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">研究团队将之前的 SOTA 压缩方法 CriticalKV 中的平均聚合替换为防御性聚合，实现了全新的压缩方法</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;DefensiveKV&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">及其层间调度增强版</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;Layer-DefensiveKV</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。实验结果令人震撼：仅需两行代码的修改，就实现了显著的性能飞跃。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.4003569303985723\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1681\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503539516\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9f874f65&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqHXrojfHRMQYTrd8NPcbyJGG2qlltRSzPH6icChGqELlW94XSocplmEYGKdaXQYX8sjBgMLXEsJjAyXMndYOecMxBCenBblZXSk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">图 5：DefensiveKV 和 Layer-DefensiveKV 展示了领先的性能</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">文章中的测评横跨 7 个任务领域、18 个数据集、3 个不同规模的主流开源模型，一致性地刷新了 KV Cache 压缩的性能边界。例如，在 Llama-3.1-8B 模型 20% cache 预算的严苛压缩条件下，相比最强基线 CriticalKV（质量损失 9.6%），DefensiveKV 将损失降至 4.1%（</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">2.3 倍提升</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">），而 Layer-DefensiveKV 更是仅为 2.1%（</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">4.6 倍提升</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.4388888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503539517\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7b2b93c0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqHHRTIEKEReozwz7jptBhYM59DPiagwNyRAibPaicFgWt4UMzSoE4aibsVhdyNPWibduNjj0s8UlMWT1oficAOsiafVOcPtK3EIlOMKibM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">图 6：DefensiveKV 和 Layer-DefensiveKV 平均压缩损失极低</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这项工作的重要价值不仅在于算法性能提升，更在于</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">重新定义了 KV Cache 压缩的优化目标</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。它首次揭示了现有算法底层稳定性假设的本质脆弱性，开创性地将最坏风险控制思想引入该领域，为后续研究指明了全新方向：与其设计更精密的重要性指标，不如构建更具防御性的策略来对抗底层假设的脆弱性。这种防御性思维 —— 宁可错留、不可错删 —— 或许是通往真正鲁棒长上下文推理的关键钥匙。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">DefensiveKV 的全部代码已经开源，提供了完整的实验环境配置、打包数据集、评测代码以及详细的使用文档。团队额外特别提供了一个一小时内完成的迷你复现 Demo，感受防御性聚合带来的强大性能。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">一小时极速验证：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">基于 10% RULER benchmark 的快速评测脚本，在单张 RTX 4090 上即可在 1 小时内完成 DefensiveKV 和 Layer-DefensiveKV 在 20% cache size 下的性能验证。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">性能真相揭秘：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过纠正先前 benchmark 的评测缺陷，团队发现 SnapKV 在 20% 压缩率下的真实得分仅为 39.0，彻底打破了此前 \"无损压缩\" 的幻象。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">算法持续提升：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">感受 KV Cache 压缩领域近一年来从 AdaKV 到 CriticalKV 再到 DefensiveKV 的迭代提升，性能从 39.0 一路提升至 91.4。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">可叠加增益：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Defensive Aggregation 作为正交化方法，可与现有各类 KV Cache 压缩技术无缝结合，实现性能的持续提升。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"1541\" data-imgfileid=\"503520319\" data-ratio=\"2.6657407407407407\" style=\"height: 1541px;width: 578px;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=948ec4f5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqHq8Ydib5GB5GoQfic2cA3ZrDPzEBP0q8lQGPlBViaWbIKGsGExJ89TVZcjQezDE4msmhJOvvGWnOVFJoJZN9vmib1o2rKVJcOaOno%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);text-size-adjust: auto;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;line-height: 27.2px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span mp-original-font-size=\"12\" mp-original-line-height=\"19.200000762939453\" style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 19.2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">© THE END&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);text-size-adjust: auto;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;line-height: 27.2px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span mp-original-font-size=\"12\" mp-original-line-height=\"19.200000762939453\" style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);line-height: 19.2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">转载请联系本公众号获得授权</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);text-size-adjust: auto;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;line-height: 27.2px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span mp-original-font-size=\"12\" mp-original-line-height=\"19.200000762939453\" style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);line-height: 19.2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">投稿或寻求报道：liyazhou@jiqizhixin.com</span></span></p>\n  